<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
Give us a mezz bolt  <IMG SRC="biggrin.gif" border="0"> <P>It would have the range of a wizzy bolt, do the damage of an equal level body nuke to the target, and drop an AE mezz when it lands. You'd get it in the domination line every ten levels, starting at 25. An example: <P>lvl 25 <BR>Name: Streak of Senility <BR>Damage: 73 <BR>Target: Enemy(Duh, just trying to make this look authentic) <BR>Range: 1875 <BR>Radius: 300 <BR>Duration: 45 seconds <BR>Damage Type: Energy <BR>Power Cost: 13 <BR>Casting Time: 4.0 seconds <BR>Recast Time: 20 seconds <P>(Note that the damage would be blockable, but the mezz would always go off. You can't block a mezz you sillies :P) <P><BR>I basically combined parts of the lvl 23 wizzy bolt, the lvl 24 AE mezz for he sorc, and the sorc's lvl 23 lifetap. <P>Anyway, it would let us combat the instas by striking first. Try to determine which is the healer/bard(The latter would be easy)and fire it at him. The damage would be mediocre, but it would add a much-needed buff to the mind line. Additions would come at 35 and 45 mind spec, with radii and damages increasing the same as the AE mezz and the lifetap. <P>So, what does everyone think?
</FONT>
