<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
A bolt that did damage as well as CC *and* drained life?<P>Oh, the trolls would scream "Nerf, bloody nerf".<P>But....an interesting idea, a Mez at bolt range.  What if we put our single-target Mez at bolt range?  Since it's not AE, it wouldn't be "horribly dominating" in large battles, and the only time single-targets make a difference being Duels, it wouldn't do *too* much either, just give us a better chance at getting the first move (That's all Mez does in duels anyways, either give us the first move, or if used halfway through, lets us recoup, in which case range is usually not a factor if halfway through the fight already).<P>Plus, a bolt single-target mez would give our castable a slight niche of importance over instants, which have the same range of our current castables.
</FONT>
