<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
I like the idea.  It should look really cool like a glowing ball of twisting energy.  I would propose three spells in the line.  All 3 would are single target mez spells.  An AE would unbalance mezzes but a single target only affects one person so it doesn't shaft the entire opposing army or a large chunk of it.  THis spell would allows us to possibly get the bards or healers.  It is also a much simpler idea then my Super, Duper Neato Stun idea.<P><BR>All 3 spells would be on the energy line.  They are a bolt spell so they cannot be used on someone in combat the same way a bolt works, and it can also be block by a tank using engage like a regular bolt.  Instead of damage it hits the player for a duration.  <BR>Mind Missile (lvl 25) [30sec mez] CT 3.0 Range 1700 - I know weak name. But weak names work for weak spells and will just give you more pride when you get a better one with a cool name.<P>Mind Bolt (lvl 35)[40 sec] Range 1800 CT 2.5<BR>Mind Blast(lvl 45)[50 sec] Range 1875 CT 2.5<P><BR>I really think adding damage to a mez is crazy.  It's like giving Armsman an insta heal line.<P>--------------------<P>Toadstool, THE Newbie Sorc, Kay
